<p>Hey <%= @source_user.first_name %>,</p>
 
<p>We've found you an incredible opportunity to do business with <%= @target_user.first_name %> <%= @target_user.last_name %>!</p>

<% if @match_type == "reciprocal" %>
	<p><%= @target_user.first_name %> offers <%= @matched_needs %>, and is looking for <%= @matched_offerings %>.You are looking for <%= @matched_needs %>, and offer <%= @matched_offerings %>.</p>

	<p>Sounds like a great match!</p>

<% elsif @match_type == "needs" %>
	<p><%= @target_user.first_name %> offers <%= @matched_needs %>, and may just be the person you are looking for.</p>
<% elsif @match_type == "offerings" %>
	<p><%= @target_user.first_name %> is looking for <%= @matched_offerings %> which you said that you offer.</p>
<% end %>

<p>Here are a few ways you can contact <%= @target_user.first_name %>:</p>

<p>
<% if @target_user.skype? %>
Contact <%= @target_user.first_name %> using Skype:   <%= @target_user.skype %><br/>
<% end %>

<% if @target_user.email? %>
Contact <%= @target_user.first_name %> using Email:   <%= @target_user.email %><br/>
<% end %>

<% if @target_user.phone? %>
Contact <%= @target_user.first_name %> using Phone:   <%= @target_user.phone %>
<% end %>
</p>